==Transportation== {{See also|Baghestan City and Suburbs Bus Organization}} The city is served by buses from the municipal-run [[Baghestan City and Suburbs Bus Organization]], connecting the city to [[Shahriar, Tehran Province|Shahriar]] and [[Tehran]].
